				<td colspan="2"><span>OMG I cannot begin to say what an awsome song this is for a bard.  I use it all the time.  I have rujarkan lute of battle from ldon EC. Cost you bout 540 raid points.  I believe its a 2.6 mod to strings. any who ... let me begin.
<br />

<br />
AE group : With above stated lute, this song produces 114 damage per mob per pulse with slowing the mob near 60 %.  And no limit to the number of mobs it effects. Even if mobs get past the cleric or chanter stunns and begin to attack your casters, they are all slowed And the only time I have gotten a resist message on this was on some EOM mobs when my guild AE's VT for clearing to named.  Mix this with Dennon's ( forgot name but is poison DOT lvl 59 ) i get to deal near 200 pts damage per tick. One fadding memmories drops all of your aggro and your free to mix chorus of marr for mana / heal or Psalm of veeshan for resist and a good DS for more dps.
<br />

<br />
Faction work : Need to work giant faction but dont want to KS everyone of the mid 40's doing exp work there ?  or if your doing chardok faction and deside to kill everything in mines of nurga ? Get a healer druid or cleric will do cause they have very good AE spells, pull a train, dot them to death with slow and poison, and cut your time in half. Dont even have to melee at all, keep lute in main hand for more damage and let the caster / healer finnish them off with thier DD PB aoe once they are stacked on top of you.
<br />

<br />
Powerleveling : Got a lvl 43 buddy that you wish could play more with you or app your guild but he / she is not high enough of level ? use this and your poison dot and head to lower guk / DL / or dulak harbor. I was pulling trains of 30 + mobs. with 43 necro / 65 cleric / 65 bard ( me ). Cleric lands super elixer on inc ( very little to no aggro heal ) and I stack the mobs till i can get a non interupted Melody of Mischief to land on the pack. Instantly dropped 60 % of all damage and am able to channel through songs to dot / slow. Once mob aggro set the cleric / Necro let em have it with thier ae songs. She was getting 6 to 12 percent per pull.  Very nice plats there with the gem drop rate.
<br />

<br />
Cleric epic : what a pain in the arse the shard camps are now with like a 1 % chance per mob drop rate on pearlescent shards.  Get a group of full casters and healer and pbae skyfire at the burning woods zone. Cleric lands heal over time on pull inc and they the casters wear em out for those PITA shards.
<br />

<br />
Raid PBAE : Our guild recently entered Plane of fire ON Tholuxe Paells server /hug Crusaders Valorous and we have religously used AE tactics when gearing up and clearing to named mobs.  I would shrink two times and stand right next to the AE taunt warrior in pin corner. First cast of MoM gets me aggro but they are all slowed. Simply fade off and never get hit again.</span></td>
